      <h2>Our Mission <i class="fa-solid fa-bullseye"></i></h2>
      <p>
        At Healthcare+, our mission is to bring high-quality healthcare services to underserved communities in rural areas. 
        We believe in bridging the healthcare gap by delivering accessible, affordable, and sustainable medical care to those who need it most. 
        Our team is dedicated to improving the well-being of rural populations through various healthcare initiatives, mobile clinics, telemedicine, and education programs.
      </p>
      <h2>Our Vision <i class="fa-solid fa-eye"></i></h2>
      <p>
        Our vision is to create a healthier and more empowered rural community where everyone has access to the healthcare they deserve. 
        We strive to develop partnerships, foster community involvement, and utilize technology to enhance healthcare delivery. 
        Through innovation and compassion, we aim to bring lasting impact and improve lives in rural regions.
      </p>

      <h2>Our Values <i class="fa-solid fa-person-rays"></i></i></h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Accessibility: Ensuring everyone in rural areas can access quality healthcare.</li>
        <li>Compassion: Caring for patients with empathy and respect.</li>
        <li>Innovation: Leveraging technology to make healthcare services more effective.</li>
        <li>Community Focus: Working together with local communities to understand and address their unique healthcare needs.</li>
        <li>Empowerment: Educating communities and building their capacity to take control of their health.</li>
      </ul>
